## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and cache ##
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Ignore build output ##
bin/
obj/
Debug/
Release/
x64/
x86/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]*/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64*/

## Ignore publish profiles ##
Properties/PublishProfiles/

## Ignore NuGet packages ##
*.nupkg
packages/
*.snupkg

## Ignore logs ##
*.log

## Ignore wwwroot auto-generated cache ##
wwwroot/lib/
wwwroot/node_modules/

## Ignore Node modules ##
node_modules/

## Ignore Rider / JetBrains ##
.idea/
*.sln.iml

## Ignore VS Code settings ##
.vscode/

## Ignore SQL dev files ##
*.mdf
*.ldf

## Ignore backups ##
*.bak

## Ignore ReSharper cache ##
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user

## Ignore Image Cache ##
*.jpg.tmp
*.png.tmp
